title: Eliminates the annual service charge for distinctive plates for members of volunteer ambulance services and replaces it with a one time service charge
summary: Eliminates the annual service charge for distinctive plates for members of volunteer ambulance services and replaces it with a one time service charge of twenty dollars.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the vehicle and traffic law, in relation to eliminating the annual service charge for distinctive plates for members of volunteer ambulance services
